{{multiple issues|{{notability|music|date=May 2015}}{{more footnotes|date=May 2015}} {{one source|date=May 2015}} {{refimprove|date=May 2015}} }} {{Infobox musical artist <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject_Musicians --> | name = Grup Munzur | image = | caption = | image_size = | background = group_or_band | alias = | origin = [[İzmir]], [[Turkey]] | instrument = | genre = [[Folk rock]], [[folk music|folk]], [[protest music]], [[Left-wing politics|left]], [[Music and politics|political music]], [[türkü]] | occupation = | years_active = 1992–present | label = | associated_acts = | website = http://www.grupmunzur.com/ | current_members = Özlem Gerçek, Mahir Çelebi, Ercan Duman | past_members = | notable_instruments = [[bağlama]], [[davul]], [[zurna]], [[flute]] }}
'''Grup Munzur''' is a [[Turkey|Turkish]] band known for their [[protest music|protest]] [[songwriting]] and some of the group members were arrested and tried for their artistic activities.<ref>[http://www.ozgurdersim.com/haber/grup-munzur-uyelerine-10-ay-hapis-cezasi-1355.htm Grup Munzur üyelerine 10 ay hapis cezası] ozgurdersim.com</ref><ref>[http://www.radikal.com.tr/turkiye/5_slogan_attin_25_yil_hapis_yatmalisin-1082449 5 slogan attin 25 yil hapis yatmalisin] radikal.com.tr</ref> Grup Munzur was founded in 1992 in [[İzmir]].<ref>[http://www.grupmunzur.com/hakkimizda/ Hakkımızda]. grupmunzur.com</ref> Grup Munzur has yearly performed at ''Munzur Doğa ve Kültür Festivali'' in [[Tunceli Province]].<ref>[http://dersimnews.com/kultur/13-munzur-kultur-ve-doga-festivali-programi.html 13. Munzur Kültür ve Doğa Festivali Programı] dersimnews.com</ref><ref>[http://www.bianet.org/bianet/sanat/157432-14-munzur-festivali-programi-aciklandi 14 Munzur Festivali Programi] bianet.org</ref> Musicians of Grup Munzur are known of their sympathy to the [[Maoist insurgency in Turkey|maoist movement]].<ref>[http://www.ozgurgelecek.net/manset-haberler/1782-pnar-aydnlara-yine-ve-yeniden-kaypakkaya-soruturmas.html Pınar Aydınlar’a “yine ve yeniden” Kaypakkaya soruşturması!] ozgurgelecek.net</ref>
