{{Use DMY dates|date=September 2017}} The '''Raigam Tele'es Best Teledrama Art Director Award''' is presented annually in Sri Lanka by the Kingdom of Raigam associated with many commercial brands for the best Sri Lankan art director of the year in television screen.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.srilankanewslive.com/news/security/item/12553-it-s-tele-es-time-again |title=It’s Tele’es time again! |publisher=Srilankanewslive.com |accessdate=11 March 2017}}</ref>
The award was first given in 2005. Following is a list of the winners of this prestigious title since then.
